subject: Sex Crimes
Football (College)
Heisman Trophy
lead_paragraph: Florida State’s Jameis Winston, who faced scrutiny this season after being accused of rape, finished 1,501 points ahead of A J McCarron for the seventh-largest victory margin in Heisman history.
